  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the beginning, of course, I was very-- a very-- cooperative, in terms of-- apart from the childish tantrums and childish-- in fact, I was sometimes rebellious because my father wouldn't wake me up at 12:00 at night to go to the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He let me sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had [INAUDIBLE] and didn't wake me up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I made scandals for overlooking me and treating me as a kid, when I felt I already had to be part of the congregations and so on-- the ambitions of a young boy and so on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, the bar mitzvah was still observed, with all the formalities, although not in the way it's done here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't have to have teachers to teach me the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't have to learn by heart, things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when-- and I made my first speech at afternoon table in [INAUDIBLE], without having written out on a piece of paper, and so on, in the presence of the headmaster of the school and the classes.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But then, at the age of 14, after putting on [INAUDIBLE] every morning, religiously, I rebelled.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "By that time, I went-- I left and I went into gymnasium, which was an institution of a different nature.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was already in keeping with my understanding of what I wanted to be, what I aimed to be, and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one of the first things that went was my attendance on Shabbat morning in shul.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I stopped going with Father to shul, which was a terrible blow to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I understood that it was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
